Old school tatooine start? Hot mama pajamas.  Well he goes to space early, leaving luke at kessel in r2/red5 and puts dash at tattooine.  I set up my senate and draw up for things like blast door controls, and my ships.  At one point he is about to drop mirax with squadron assignments, but she isn&#39;t there which disappoints me because I would&#39;ve dropped ship, got rid of dash and beat down on her.  Instead, I wait another turn and drop baron with thrawn in chimera, 3 destiny, don&#39;t shoot, to his one destiny&#8230; 17 card overflow &#8230; in space&#8230;  noice.  This deck is nasty.  At one point I drain big and he plays control to cancel it, so I play my nicely held limited so he cant cancel it out of lost pile. And at the end he drops talon and melas to the ground and I drop maul and finish him off and pull in the win by 22 forces.<br />
