Finally, and perhaps most importantly - the Canadians, for being the most amazing group of card players ever, and just the coolest guys all around.  Dinosaur pipeweedslap megasex beatdown props to all you guys.<br />
Ty for hooking me up with an ounee ta even if I had to give up mad lotr rares.<br />
<br />
<br />
